import React from 'react'; const TravelerWeather = ({ weatherData, weather, city, windData }) => (
{Math.round(weatherData.temp)}°C

{weather.description}

Wind: {windData.speed} mph

Sunrise: {new Date(city.sunrise * 1000).toLocaleTimeString()}

Sunset: {new Date(city.sunset * 1000).toLocaleTimeString()}

); export default TravelerWeather;
